{"tid":1091106,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[警犬] YoYo：謝謝認真調查還我清白","createTime":"2019-04-04T02:11:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-04T02:14:03.000Z","uid":56881,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"72df2505cf93328782dcd60dceb08bf85a8e4cdf","tid":1091106,"uid":56881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T02:11:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/yoyo-%E8%AC%9D%E8%AC%9D%E8%AA%8D%E7%9C%9F%E8%AA%BF%E6%9F%A5%E9%82%84%E6%88%91%E6%B8%85%E7%99%BD-214500282.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2Fyoyo-%25E8%25AC%259D%25E8%25AC%259D%25E8%25AA%258D%25E7%259C%259F%25E8%25AA%25BF%25E6%259F%25A5%25E9%2582%2584%25E6%2588%2591%25E6%25B8%2585%25E7%2599%25BD-214500282.html&d=xTo9lt5%2FMO3GrXFnFHQdvFJiVKGJ8LWvq%2BeQg4NrPGo%3D&h=a24dd0b8\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/yoyo-%E8%AC%9D%E8%AC%9D%E8%AA%8D%E7%9C%9F%E8%AA%BF%E6%9F%A5%E9%82%84%E6%88%91%E6%B8%85%E7%99%BD-214500282.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/kREFj8dEQMOT9Xm8Al6KDw--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw/https://media.zenfs.com/zh-TW/thesun.hk.com/0aac7c34e13e3fba256252eabe875d3f\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FkREFj8dEQMOT9Xm8Al6KDw--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-TW%2Fthesun.hk.com%2F0aac7c34e13e3fba256252eabe875d3f&h=189e5236&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n伍淑怡事發後向投訴警察課投訴。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】女模特兒伍淑怡（YoYo）自去年六月在社交網站公開被警員「抄牌」（索取手提電話）後，不但承受不少壓力，期間更受到滋擾，包括收到匿名信件辱罵，但她未有後悔，站出來是不希望有下一個受害者。<br />\n<br />\nYoYo早前在社交網上載由警方寄來的信件，指她投訴的事件，經調查後獲證明屬實，並會對涉事警員進行適當處分，她留言指，「我伍淑怡從來都唔會誣告他人，謝謝認真調查，讓我得到清白！」<br />\n<br />\n公開事件後遭辱罵<br />\n<br />\nYoYo昨晚向本報指，自她去年六月公開事件，一直受到滋擾，包括去年七月生日時，曾收到有人用紅筆寫的匿名信，罵她投訴警員，內容包括：「祝你今世永無生日，不得好死！」她之後曾報警。此外，她社交網頁亦經常遭人留言辱罵，一度令她擔心個人安全，更因此搬屋，但她並不後悔，因不希望有下個一個受害者。<br />\n<br />\n對男警說謊感憤怒<br />\n<br />\n對於監警會指涉事男警三度「講大話」，令她感到憤怒，但既然對方已受到應有制裁，她亦釋懷，但以後認識異性時會加倍小心。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />係咪太柒唔想認<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54f12758853264faef8c503b363b198d9b9488b2","tid":1091106,"uid":102732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T02:14:03.000Z","msg":"辣殺"}]}